months. Our management for the cases associated with malignant tumor and cardiac 
diseases as next. We perform the cardiac operation for the case whose life 
expectancy is longer than 1 year. We perform the cardiac operation before the 
operation of malignant tumor. We perform the operation for malignant tumor as 
soon as the patient had recovered from the cardiac operation. We would not 
perform any adjuvant therapy before completion of the operation for the heart 
and tumor.

